50|$|In 2010, the GLC {{introduced}} the nationwide <b>Public</b> <b>Authorities</b> Information Clearinghouse (PAIC), {{designed to help}} government officials, public interest groups, and others navigate documents that pertain to the operation of government of <b>public</b> <b>authorities.</b> A blog on <b>public</b> <b>authorities</b> was launched in 2011.|$|R
